@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rncogb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.sin((v0 + 0.60 * tmp + 0.92)))
    v1 = wp.sin((v0 * wp.cos(tmp + 0.81)))
    v1 = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.20 * tmp + 0.79)) * (wp.abs(v2 + 0.18) - (v1 + 0.61 - v2 + 0.78)))
    v1 = wp.sin(0.23)
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.exp(v0 + 0.69)) - wp.abs(tmp))
    tmp = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.49 + tmp + 1.00)) / wp.abs(v2))
    v0 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.99 - v1 + 0.83)) * wp.sin(v0))
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.sin((tmp + 0.53 - tmp + 0.25)))
    data[tid] = v0
